2026-03-30T07:07:58.902Z JOY-0095 item.created "joy ai setup does not clean stale files on update" [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
2026-03-30T07:08:05.351Z JOY-0095 comment.added "When joy ai setup regenerates files for a configured tool, it only creates and updates files but never removes stale ones. If an agent is renamed or removed between versions, the old file remains in the tool directory (e.g. .claude/agents/old-name.md). Fix: when the version header in existing files does not match the running binary version, remove the Joy-managed subdirectories (agents/, skills/joy/, prompts/) and regenerate from scratch. Preserve user-owned files (CLAUDE.md content outside joy markers, settings.json)." [horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
